V0703_01_00_00_0.text: My Sogetsu Style has proved successful for generations!

V0703_01_00_01_0.text: I look forward to facing your challenge!

V0703_01_00_02_0.text: As president of Goha #7, I'll defend the honor of my school!

V0703_01_00_03_0.text: If we are to Duel, we must give nothing less than our best!

V0703_01_00_04_0.text: This is one Rush Duel that I intend to win!

V0703_01_00_05_0.text: Perhaps this is the moment when I change my style!

V0703_01_00_06_0.text: Rush Dueling against you is a challenge I enjoy, Yuga!

V0703_01_00_07_0.text:
Very well, Luke!
I accept your Duel!

V0703_01_00_08_0.text:
Romin!
If we are to Duel, we must both give our very best!

V0703_01_00_09_0.text: "Oh my! How can I Duel my friend?" is what you're thinking!

V0703_01_00_10_0.text:
I know you're not easy to defeat.
But I refuse to lose!

V0703_01_00_11_0.text: I must evolve my Duel to come out victorious!

V0703_01_00_12_0.text: Only a practitioner of tradition is worthy of Dueling you.

V0703_01_00_14_0.text: Your sloppiness is dangerous and unacceptable!

V0703_03_00_00_0.text: I'll use my advantage to create an insurmountable lead!

V0703_03_00_01_0.text: I'll make sure you won't get another turn!

V0703_03_00_04_0.text:
You're playing well...
But will it last?

V0703_03_00_05_0.text: I may be hanging on by a thread, but I am hanging on!

V0703_05_00_00_0.text: This draw is the beginning of my comeback!

V0703_06_01_02_0.text: That's what I was waiting for!

V0703_07_09_00_0.text: I'll use this card I Set earlier!

V0703_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0703_11_12_00_0.text: I shall Fusion Summon a monster!

V0703_16_00_01_0.text: This Duel has come to a close!

V0703_21_00_00_0.text: There really is nothing you can do.

V0703_21_00_04_1.text:
How am I going to get out of this?
I'm in so much trouble!

V0703_21_00_05_1.text: I must survive this turn if I want another chance!

V0703_28_00_00_0.text: I have learned to avoid distractions to focus on victory!

V0703_28_00_01_0.text: The Sogetsu Style teaches there's always a path to success!

V0703_28_00_02_0.text: Though Rush Duels go against tradition, it's so fun to play!

V0703_28_00_03_0.text: My adventures with Yuga and Luke taught me a few new tricks!

V0703_28_00_04_0.text:
Did you notice all the risks I was taking?
I feel so alive!

V0703_28_00_05_0.text: Thanks to our Rush Duel, I've broken out of my shell!

V0703_28_00_06_0.text: Rush Duels are truly spectacular, Yuga!

V0703_28_00_07_0.text: As long as I'm around, you won't take control of the school!

V0703_28_00_08_0.text: It would've been disrespectful if I went easy on you, Romin.

V0703_28_00_09_0.text: I parried every move you made, Yuran!

V0703_29_00_00_0.text: Isn't it against school rules to be this powerful?

V0703_29_00_01_0.text: I have tarnished the honor of the Sogetsu Style!

V0703_29_00_02_0.text:
I lost...
I don't deserve to be student council president!

V0703_29_00_03_0.text: This is one outcome I did not foresee!

V0703_29_00_04_0.text: I must learn to shine in the spotlight - for Rino and Rayne.

V0703_29_00_05_0.text: The creator of Rush Duels cannot be taken lightly!

V0703_29_00_06_0.text:
I admit defeat, Luke...
But you can't be president.

V0703_29_00_07_0.text: I can tell you practiced hard - just like you do with music!

V0703_29_00_09_1.text: I always wanted to say that.

V0703_29_00_11_0.text: Only a real alien could come up with those strategies.

V0703_29_00_12_0.text:
Well done, Yuran...
You bested me...

V0703_33_00_00_0.text:
You don't know what I'm planning?
Allow me to educate you!

V0703_33_00_01_0.text: I've never been more determined to win this Duel!

V0703_33_00_02_0.text: I can see the path to victory!

V0703_33_00_03_0.text: This strategy has been perfected over generations!

V0703_33_00_04_0.text: Witness the heart of the Sogetsu Style!

V0703_34_00_00_0.text:
I still have a card to turn this around-
Wait, I don't! Noo!

V0703_34_00_03_0.text:
That's against the rules!
See me after school!

V0703_34_00_04_0.text: If I change my style, I still have a chance to shine!

V0703_34_00_05_0.text: Never forget that I am always focused!

V0703_34_00_06_0.text:
Allow me to explain!
We must draw until we have five cards!

V0703_34_00_07_0.text: The selfish ones never survive a zombie apocalypse!

V0703_34_00_09_0.text: The Professor Gavin, at your service!

V0703_34_00_10_0.text:
When I say DJ, you say G!
DJ! ...DJ? ...Anyone?

V0703_34_00_11_0.text: I abandoned my Sogetsu Style, but I’m bombing out here...

V0703_35_00_00_0.text:
I'm Gavin Sogetsu!
Student council president of Goha #7!

V0703_35_00_01_0.text: You can count on the Sogetsu Style to save the day!

V0703_36_00_00_0.text: I believe you will end the Duel this turn!

V0703_36_00_01_0.text: Bring this match to a grand finish!

V0703_36_00_02_0.text:
You're up.
I can't wait to see what you do!

V0703_36_00_04_0.text:
This is worse than bad!
This is horrible!

V0703_36_00_05_0.text:
If their attack succeeds, we lose!
Find a way to survive!

V0703_36_00_06_0.text: It all rests on you, Yuga!
